---
title: "Hive shutting down North American Servers"
created: 2021-11-13 13:58:00
integrations:
  - hive
homeassistant: ">2021.11.0"
---
From Tuesday November 30th 2021, Hive will not be offering services in North America. 

Hive have decided to shut down the North American servers that support their lights, sensors, thermostats, and other IOT devices. EU servers will continue to work (for now).
 
Link to announcement on Hive's support page: https://www.hivehome.com/us/support
